Start a new profile at a given point.



```js
startProfileAt(to: [number], sketch_surface: SketchSurface, tag?: TagDeclarator) -> SketchGroup
```

### Examples

```js
const exampleSketch = startSketchOn('XZ')
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> line([10, 0], %)
  |> line([0, 10], %)
  |> line([-10, 0], %)
  |> close(%)

const example = extrude(5, exampleSketch)
```
